{"tid":2379731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【12.1 紅磡】相隔逾年被控暴動　兼職女社工發燒留院　押後再訊","createTime":"2021-01-25T11:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T12:37:21.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e2ee4f89b5840157655abc46a4fce0382daccdc8","tid":2379731,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:52:50.000Z","msg":"2019 年 12 月 1 日，網民在尖沙咀發起「毋忘初心大遊行」，其後九龍各區爆發衝突。相隔逾一年，25 歲兼職女社工「踢保」後被控暴動罪，今（23 日）在九龍城裁判法院首次提堂，被告缺席聆訊。控方庭上透露被告發燒，仍在東區醫院留醫，案件押至 1 月 28 日或更早出院日再訊，<span class=\"red\">期間還押警方看管</span>。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，當晚有人衝入黃埔附近商場，破壞「元氣壽司」、「優品 360」等店舖。被告晚上約 8 時被捕，警誡下保持沉默。"},{"pid":"69b436761c397ecb09558086fa6dd3f2554d4b34","tid":2379731,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:52:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/12-1-%E7%B4%85%E7%A3%A1-%E7%9B%B8%E9%9A%94%E9%80%BE%E5%B9%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95-%E5%85%BC%E8%81%B7%E5%A5%B3%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5%E7%99%BC%E7%87%92%E7%95%99%E9%99%A2-%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F12-1-%25E7%25B4%2585%25E7%25A3%25A1-%25E7%259B%25B8%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595-%25E5%2585%25BC%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2587%2592%25E7%2595%2599%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=5e5a844c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F12-1-%25E7%25B4%2585%25E7%25A3%25A1-%25E7%259B%25B8%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595-%25E5%2585%25BC%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2587%2592%25E7%2595%2599%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2586%258D%2